metadata.name: Vector Resources Limited
metadata.description: Vector Resources Limited operates as a gold exploration and development company. The company explores for gold deposits. It owns 70% interest in the Maniema Gold project; and Adidi-Kanga Gold project, which covers an area of 5,033 square kilometers and 13 licenses located in the Maniema Province, the Democratic Republic of Congo. The company was incorporated in 2004 and is based in South Perth, Australia.
